**THE NEW WESTMINSTER DOWNTOWN RESIDENTS ASSOCIATION**

**Public Meeting**

**WHEN:** Wednesday January 2nd, 2019

**TIME** : 7:00pm-9:00 pm

**WHERE:** Holy Trinity Cathedral at 514 Carnarvon St.

**Guest Speakers**

**Larry Church and Ron Spence 7:00-7:15**

Larry and Ron would like to discuss with the residents bringing the Show and Shine back to Columbia Street for 2020 in concert with the Hyack Festival.

**Mayor Jonathan Cote**

**7:15-9:00**

 ![](data:image/*;base64,)

Join us in welcoming our Mayor Jonathan Cote as he will present his councils vision for the upcoming year and answer your questions in an informal Q&amp;A.
